@startuml PanelAdminSuccessFlow
title TIMELAPSE - Painel Admin - Fluxo de Sucesso (UC003 - RF009)
actor Admin
participant Browser
participant ControlPlane
participant AuthAPI
participant LicenseManager

Admin -> Browser: Acessa app.timelapse.dev
Browser -> ControlPlane: GET /login

Admin -> Browser: Informa Email (Magic Link)
Browser -> ControlPlane: POST /auth/magic-link
ControlPlane -> AuthAPI: Enviar Magic Link
AuthAPI -> Admin: Email recebido

Admin -> Browser: Clica no Link
Browser -> ControlPlane: GET /auth/verify?token=...
ControlPlane -> AuthAPI: Valida Token
AuthAPI -> ControlPlane: JWT + User + Orgs

ControlPlane -> Browser: Redireciona /admin
Browser -> ControlPlane: GET /admin/dashboard (JWT)
ControlPlane -> LicenseManager: Verificar licença da org
LicenseManager -> ControlPlane: Pro/Enterprise ativa

ControlPlane -> Browser: Painel administrativo
Browser -> Admin: Dashboard - Times, membros, analytics
@enduml
